commit.message: Radius of nearby users can be specified

Reduced logging to a minimum
Now just logs user connect/disconnect
Fixed issues with data being empty
Separated websocket connections from client data
Started on shortest distances and nearby users
Using broadcasting now to send data to clients
Fixed bug with empty arrays in client data
Client data is now an array

Fixed double-send issue
Refactored some code

Updated server to handle user data
Also updates all clients when data changes
